Setup: Download Java 8 and set it up including JAVA_HOME

To start server: ./sbt run (Missing dependencies are downloaded here the first time, will take a while )

To run tests: ./sbt test

Verify Behavior:

Post base case:  curl -v -X POST http://localhost:9000

Post with headers: curl -v -X POST -H "Accept: application/json" http://localhost:9000

Simple Get: curl -v http://localhost:9000

Get with Accept Headers: curl -v -H "Accept: application/json" http://localhost:9000

